="ssrcss-mysbf6-ComponentWrapper-CrossheadComponentWrapper e1xue1i84"><h2 class="ssrcss-qozapo-StyledHeading e1fj1fc10">1. £10,000 fines for failing to self-isolate</h2></div><div data-component="text-block" class="ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper e1xue1i83"><div class="ssrcss-3z08n3-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi2"><p>The government has said it will introduce a new legal duty requiring people in England to self-isolate if they test positive for coronavirus, or are traced as a close contact. From 28 September, <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-54221953" class="ssrcss-hiczm3-InlineLink e1no5rhv0">those who refuse an order to self-isolate could be fined up to £10,000.</a> The new measures also include a one-off support payment of £500 for those on lower incomes. <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-54214752" class="ssrcss-hiczm3-InlineLink e1no5rhv0">The PM is still considering tightening restrictions further</a> after a surge in cases across the UK - another 4,422 cases were recorded on Saturday.</p></div></div><div data-component="image-block" class="ssrcss-18mjolk-ComponentWrapper e1xue1i80"><figure class="ssrcss-2y05cd-StyledFigure e34k3c20"><div class="ssrcss-kwaqyc-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c22"><span class="ssrcss-1ku6u16-Placeholder e16icw910"><span><noscript><img alt="Chart shows daily cases are continuing to rise" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/17D5D/production/_114492679_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_19sep-nc.png 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/17D5D/production/_114492679_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_19sep-nc.png 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/17D5D/production/_114492679_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_19sep-nc.png 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/17D5D/production/_114492679_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_19sep-nc.png 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/17D5D/production/_114492679_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_19sep-nc.png 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/17D5D/production/_114492679_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_19sep-nc.png 976w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/2048/cpsprodpb/17D5D/production/_114492679_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_19sep-nc.png" width="2048" height="1440.3600900225056" loading="lazy" class="ssrcss-evoj7m-Image ee0ct7c0"/></noscript></span></span></div></figure></div><div data-component="image-block" class="ssrcss-18mjolk-ComponentWrapper e1xue1i80"><figure class="ssrcss-2y05cd-StyledFigure e34k3c20"><div class="ssrcss-kwaqyc-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c22"><span class="ssrcss-1ix1qms-Placeholder e16icw910"><span><noscript><img alt="Presentational white space" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/17B75/production/_105914179_blank_white_space-nc.png 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/17B75/production/_105914179_blank_white_space-nc.png 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/17B75/production/_105914179_blank_white_space-nc.png 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/17B75/production/_105914179_blank_white_space-nc.png 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/17B75/production/_105914179_blank_white_space-nc.png 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/17B75/production/_105914179_blank_white_space-nc.png 976w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/17B75/production/_105914179_blank_white_space-nc.png" width="624" height="1" loading="lazy" class="ssrcss-evoj7m-Image ee0ct7c0"/></noscript></span></span></div></figure></div><div data-component="image-block" class="ssrcss-18mjolk-ComponentWrapper e1xue1i80"><figure class="ssrcss-2y05cd-StyledFigure e34k3c20"><div class="ssrcss-kwaqyc-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c22"><span class="ssrcss-1iqsg44-Placeholder e16icw910"><span><noscript><img alt="Short presentational grey line" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 976w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png" width="624" height="23" loading="lazy" class="ssrcss-evoj7m-Image ee0ct7c0"/></noscript></span></span></div></figure></div><div data-component="crosshead-block" class="ssrcss-mysbf6-ComponentWrapper-CrossheadComponentWrapper e1xue1i84"><h2 class="ssrcss-qozapo-StyledHeading e1fj1fc10">2. BA accused of snubbing refund request</h2></div><div data-component="text-block" class="ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper e1xue1i83"><div class="ssrcss-3z08n3-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi2"><p>Lesley Anderson had been due to fly from Glasgow to London to celebrate her birthday, but disruption caused by the pandemic meant her British Airways flights were cancelled. She says a voucher was issued &quot;automatically&quot; after she selected &quot;cancel and refund flight&quot;. BA has said there is &quot;no way&quot; that vouchers can be issued without customers requesting them. You can read the full story <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-54160376" class="ssrcss-hiczm3-InlineLink e1no5rhv0">here</a> from Ms Anderson, who is <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-54059004" class="ssrcss-hiczm3-InlineLink e1no5rhv0">the latest person to accuse the airline of misleading its customers.</a></p></div></div><div data-component="image-block" class="ssrcss-18mjolk-ComponentWrapper e1xue1i80"><figure class="ssrcss-2y05cd-StyledFigure e34k3c20"><div class="ssrcss-kwaqyc-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c22"><span class="ssrcss-1xtcmof-Placeholder e16icw910"><span><noscript><img alt="British Airways plane" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/817C/production/_107784133_ba.jpg 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/817C/production/_107784133_ba.jpg 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/817C/production/_107784133_ba.jpg 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/817C/production/_107784133_ba.jpg 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/817C/production/_107784133_ba.jpg 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/817C/production/_107784133_ba.jpg 976w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/817C/production/_107784133_ba.jpg" width="976" height="549" loading="lazy" class="ssrcss-evoj7m-Image ee0ct7c0"/></noscript></span></span><span class="ssrcss-1ecljvk-StyledFigureCopyright e34k3c23"><span class="ssrcss-oyqyoe-VisuallyHidden e1y6uwnp0">image copyright</span>Getty Images</span></div></figure></div><div data-component="image-block" class="ssrcss-18mjolk-ComponentWrapper e1xue1i80"><figure class="ssrcss-2y05cd-StyledFigure e34k3c20"><div class="ssrcss-kwaqyc-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c22"><span class="ssrcss-1iqsg44-Placeholder e16icw910"><span><noscript><img alt="Short presentational grey line" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 976w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png" width="624" height="23" loading="lazy" class="ssrcss-evoj7m-Image ee0ct7c0"/></noscript></span></span></div></figure></div><div data-component="crosshead-block" class="ssrcss-mysbf6-ComponentWrapper-CrossheadComponentWrapper e1xue1i84"><h2 class="ssrcss-qozapo-StyledHeading e1fj1fc10">3. Singapore rolls out tracing tokens</h2></div><div data-component="text-block" class="ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper e1xue1i83"><div class="ssrcss-3z08n3-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi2"><p>Thousands of devices which can track where a person has been and who they have interacted with <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-54143015" class="ssrcss-hiczm3-InlineLink e1no5rhv0">are being distributed in Singapore.</a> The small Bluetooth device is meant for those who do not own smartphones and cannot use a contact tracing app. Authorities say the token helps vulnerable groups to feel safer when out and about.</p></div></div><div data-component="media-block" class="ssrcss-18mjolk-ComponentWrapper e1xue1i80"><figure class="ssrcss-2y05cd-StyledFigure e34k3c20"><div class="ssrcss-kwaqyc-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c22"><div class="ssrcss-1uy4vn0-Container e1h75hkw0"><div data-testid="bbc-logo-wrapper" class="ssrcss-1d84lqw-LogoIconWrapper e1h75hkw2"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 210.69 60" class="ssrcss-47d2zd-StyledIcon e6m7o990" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M36.76 33.87c-2.21-.78-3.78-.78-7.12-.78h-5.18v11.79H30c4.28 0 5.61-.25 7.37-1a5.58 5.58 0 002.47-2 4.86 4.86 0 00.85-2.55 5.11 5.11 0 00-.87-3.33 6.31 6.31 0 00-3.06-2.13zM35.25 24.36a5.28 5.28 0 001.51-4.23c-.06-2.62-1.6-5-7.63-5h-4.67v11.21h3.37c3.56 0 6.01-.62 7.42-1.98z"></path><path d="M0 0v60h63.76V0zm46.69 45.76a11.33 11.33 0 01-5.3 4.24 22.16 22.16 0 01-8.89 1.64H16.72V8.41h12.21a22.73 22.73 0 019 1.44 11.34 11.34 0 014.94 4 9.73 9.73 0 011.8 5.93c0 4.09-1.77 6.94-5.51 8.