c.png 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 976w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png" width="624" height="23" loading="lazy" class="ssrcss-evoj7m-Image ee0ct7c0"/></noscript></span></span></div></figure></div><div data-component="crosshead-block" class="ssrcss-mysbf6-ComponentWrapper-CrossheadComponentWrapper e1xue1i84"><h2 class="ssrcss-qozapo-StyledHeading e1fj1fc10">4. Political party conferences in a Covid world</h2></div><div data-component="text-block" class="ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper e1xue1i83"><div class="ssrcss-3z08n3-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi2"><p>Coronavirus has robbed politicos of the chance to mingle in their hundreds at party conferences this autumn. Instead, Conservatives, Labourites and Liberal Democrats will have to watch their leaders speak via Zoom. The parties insist the events will be as vibrant and interesting as possible, but, as Labour&#x27;s gets under way this weekend, <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-54150015" class="ssrcss-hiczm3-InlineLink e1no5rhv0">what are the big things to look out for and how much has changed?</a></p></div></div><div data-component="image-block" class="ssrcss-18mjolk-ComponentWrapper e1xue1i80"><figure class="ssrcss-2y05cd-StyledFigure e34k3c20"><div class="ssrcss-kwaqyc-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c22"><span class="ssrcss-1xtcmof-Placeholder e16icw910"><span><noscript><img alt="(L-R) Sir Ed Davey, Boris Johnson, Sir Keir Starmer, Nicola Sturgeon" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/929B/production/_114413573_leaders.png 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/929B/production/_114413573_leaders.png 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/929B/production/_114413573_leaders.png 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/929B/production/_114413573_leaders.png 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/929B/production/_114413573_leaders.png 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/929B/production/_114413573_leaders.png 976w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/929B/production/_114413573_leaders.png" width="976" height="549" loading="lazy" class="ssrcss-evoj7m-Image ee0ct7c0"/></noscript></span></span><span class="ssrcss-1ecljvk-StyledFigureCopyright e34k3c23"><span class="ssrcss-oyqyoe-VisuallyHidden e1y6uwnp0">image copyright</span>PA Media</span></div></figure></div><div data-component="image-block" class="ssrcss-18mjolk-ComponentWrapper e1xue1i80"><figure class="ssrcss-2y05cd-StyledFigure e34k3c20"><div class="ssrcss-kwaqyc-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c22"><span class="ssrcss-1iqsg44-Placeholder e16icw910"><span><noscript><img alt="Short presentational grey line" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 976w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png" width="624" height="23" loading="lazy" class="ssrcss-evoj7m-Image ee0ct7c0"/></noscript></span></span></div></figure></div><div data-component="crosshead-block" class="ssrcss-mysbf6-ComponentWrapper-CrossheadComponentWrapper e1xue1i84"><h2 class="ssrcss-qozapo-StyledHeading e1fj1fc10">5. Lockdown life in photos</h2></div><div data-component="text-block" class="ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper e1xue1i83"><div class="ssrcss-3z08n3-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi2"><p>Twenty photos capturing life during lockdown have been selected as part of a competition to feature on a video with reggae band UB40. The winning image was of a deserted dual carriageway by Jack Crook. See more of <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-birmingham-54207014" class="ssrcss-hiczm3-InlineLink e1no5rhv0">the top entries.</a></p></div></div><div data-component="image-block" class="ssrcss-18mjolk-ComponentWrapper e1xue1i80"><figure class="ssrcss-2y05cd-StyledFigure e34k3c20"><div class="ssrcss-kwaqyc-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c22"><span class="ssrcss-4lxdld-Placeholder e16icw910"><span><noscript><img alt="Winning entry" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg 976w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg" width="976" height="650" loading="lazy" class="ssrcss-evoj7m-Image ee0ct7c0"/></noscript></span></span><span class="ssrcss-1ecljvk-StyledFigureCopyright e34k3c23"><span class="ssrcss-oyqyoe-VisuallyHidden e1y6uwnp0">image copyright</span>Jack Crook</span></div></figure></div><div data-component="image-block" class="ssrcss-18mjolk-ComponentWrapper e1xue1i80"><figure class="ssrcss-2y05cd-StyledFigure e34k3c20"><div class="ssrcss-kwaqyc-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c22"><span class="ssrcss-1iqsg44-Placeholder e16icw910"><span><noscript><img alt="Short presentational grey line" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png 976w" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/72FB/production/_112953492__90021446_test_grey_line_new-nc.png" width="624" height="23" loading="lazy" class="ssrcss-evoj7m-Image ee0ct7c0"/></noscript></span></span></div></figure></div><div data-component="text-block" class="ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper e1xue1i83"><div class="ssrcss-3z08n3-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi2"><p><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/articles/4g8c0mkNmM190Zl00VdXTTb/bbc-news-daily-email" class="ssrcss-hiczm3-InlineLink e1no5rhv0">Get a longer coronavirus briefing from the BBC in your inbox, each weekday morning, by signing up here.</a></p></div></div><div data-component="crosshead-block" class="ssrcss-mysbf6-ComponentWrapper-CrossheadComponentWrapper e1xue1i84"><h2 class="ssrcss-qozapo-StyledHeading e1fj1fc10">And don&#x27;t forget... </h2></div><div data-component="text-block" class="ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper e1xue1i83"><div class="ssrcss-3z08n3-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi2"><p>Find more information, advice and guides on our <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/coronavirus" class="ssrcss-hiczm3-InlineLink e1no5rhv0">coronavirus page</a>.</p></div></div><