:[{"type":"paragraph","model":{"text":"Lesley Anderson had been due to fly from Glasgow to London to celebrate her birthday, but disruption caused by the pandemic meant her British Airways flights were cancelled. She says a voucher was issued \\"automatically\\" after she selected \\"cancel and refund flight\\". BA has said there is \\"no way\\" that vouchers can be issued without customers requesting them. You can read the full story here from Ms Anderson, who is the latest person to accuse the airline of misleading its customers.","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"Lesley Anderson had been due to fly from Glasgow to London to celebrate her birthday, but disruption caused by the pandemic meant her British Airways flights were cancelled. She says a voucher was issued \\"automatically\\" after she selected \\"cancel and refund flight\\". BA has said there is \\"no way\\" that vouchers can be issued without customers requesting them. You can read the full story ","attributes":[]}},{"type":"urlLink","model":{"text":"here","locator":"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-54160376","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"here","attributes":[]}}]}},{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":" from Ms Anderson, who is ","attributes":[]}},{"type":"urlLink","model":{"text":"the latest person to accuse the airline of misleading its customers.","locator":"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-54059004","blocks":[{"type":"fragment","model":{"text":"the latest person to accuse the airline of misleading its customers.","attributes":[]}}]}}]}}]}},{"type":"image","model":{"copyright":"Getty Images","media":{"__typename":"ComponentsImage","originalSrc":"https://c.files.bbci.co.uk/817C/production/_107784133_ba.jpg","iChefRecipe":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/$recipe/cpsprodpb/817C/production/_107784133_ba.jpg","height":549,"width":976,"alt":"British Airways plane","loading":"lazy"},"blocks":[{"type":"altText","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"text","model":{"blocks":[{"type":"fragmen